District Judge Takes Madoff Trustee Suit Against ABN Amro Unit

-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 
2011-10-11T15:34:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/district-judge-takes-madoff-trustee-suit-against-abn-amro-unit.html
 U.S. District Judge Jed Rakoff in
 New York  agreed to consider the validity of a $267 million
lawsuit brought by the liquidator of Bernard L. adoff’s firm
against a unit of ABN Amro Bank NV, according to a court filing
today.  The Dutch bank asked the judge to take over its case, filed
in  bankruptcy court  by Madoff trustee Irving Picard, citing a
higher court’s ruling on limits to the power of bankruptcy
judges.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Linda Sandler in New York at 
 lsandler@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charles Carter at 
 ccarter12@bloomberg.net  